cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.NE 

This paper deals with online learning and optimization, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Specifically, it focuses on bandit feedback, which is a common setting in reinforcement learning and decision making. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves information theory and optimization, which suggest cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as possible categories.
